It’s 4th day and all I’ve been getting is rape, death and hate threats. I am clearly explaining my side of the story and how everything was taken out of context.. my brother will still learn the language.. it’s our first language for god sake.. and nowhere have I told ‘don’t learn Kannada’. I was narrating a story of my brother.
My mother tongue might not be Kannada but that doesn’t mean I am not a kannadiga.. I still am born in Coorg and am proud.
.

latestIgtvVideos.caption: Hey you guys, I wanted to shoot this since a long time and here you have it finally. I come from a village named ‘chennayanakote’ Coorg. I hope you enjoy this small tour down my village 😁

latestPosts.caption:
I find it wild how crazy the comments on part 1 are, with people saying things like, “Oh, you deserved it” or “You used it.” Baby, I was 17, 18 at the time! I was literally forced into situations I didn’t want to be in, and I was smart enough to navigate them in a way that worked in my favor.

So, stop attacking me..just pause and think. Imagine being pushed into doing things you don’t want to do or being pressured into marrying someone you barely know. I did what I had to do to survive and create the life I’m living now. You don’t have to like it, but at least understand it.

Update! Now that my parents have given me the green light - I’ve started going on a few interesting dates! Aisle has made it so much more convenient with good matches (because you haven’t seen me ranting about it on social media, right?). Honestly, I’m excited and hopeful for more dates with intention. If you’re looking for something real, you should give Aisle a shot! @aislenetwork 
#aisle #findyourkindofperfect #AD

#GraziaBeauty Food-inspired make-up trends have kicked off in the beauty landscape like no other – think of blueberry milk nails, glazed doughnut skin or strawberry girl. And with the entry of rich berry tones in our make-up during the fall season, the cranberry hue has garnered quite a bit of attention, both on runways and social media. It’s a dark berry shade that has a sort of moody and vampy aesthetic to it but looks best when worn as a monochromatic look.
